    "body" : "<p>I am sorry, I am not a pro, but if I were in this case, I would try these:</p>\n\n<p>-writing charset like this \"UTF-8\" (uppercase),\n-or instead of putting \";\" after text/xml, just putting \",\" (comma)\n-or try to use setHeader option</p>\n\n<p>Again, I am not a pro, these are all I could found by searching on the internet just now about the error you got. I hope any of this may helpful to you. </p>\n"
